// Windows resource script. Embeds resources/icons/icon.ico into the
// zorite.exe PE resource section so Windows shows the Zorite icon on the
// .exe in Explorer, the taskbar, Alt-Tab, and the Start menu. Resource
// ID 1 (IDI_APPLICATION convention) is what Windows looks up first when
// assigning a window / shortcut icon for an executable.
//
// Path is relative to this .rc file (embed-resource convention).

1 ICON "icons/icon.ico"
